public class PartitionKeyValue
extends java.lang.Object

This data class holds information about a taxonomy node, including id value (eg ModuleId or AppId value) user name (user friendly name, eg "Oracle Fusion Human Capital Management") module name (taxomomy module name, eg "HCM") module type (eg APPLICATION or LBA)
